Summary: saw 4 lights south of downtown changing positions in the sky then 2 more came in from the east to join the other 4
divs: Sighting Detailswas outside on sunday the 8th around 830 pm and saw these 4 lights south of downtown jacksonville in the distant sky. didnt really pay much attention to then until about a minute later the 4 objects changed position from making a square outline then reforming to make a straight line. after a few minutes of watching the ojects changing positions from the east i saw 2 more objects move in and join the other 4. now there are 6 objects in the sky making a triangle shape. after 15 minutes of this the objects went away.
